=== Type validation and constructors ===
strings validation: strings must be a tuple
interpolations validation: interpolations must be a tuple
strings element validation: all strings elements must be strings
interpolations element validation: all interpolations elements must be Interpolation objects
Interpolation no args: TypeError
Interpolation too many args: TypeError

=== Object representations ===
Template repr: Template(strings=('test ', ''), interpolations=(Interpolation(value=42, expression='42', conversion=None, format_spec=''),))
Interpolation repr: Interpolation(value=42, expression='x', conversion='r', format_spec='.2f')
value=42, expr=x, conv=r, fmt=.2f
Empty template: Template(strings=('',), interpolations=())

